`&lt;span class="something" data-color="black" data-bg-color="green"&gt;`
and in the CSS:
```.something[data-color] {
  /* For an element with class "something" and data attribute "data-color" */
  color: attr(data-color);
}
.something[data-bg-color] {
  /* Same with data-bg-color */
  background-color: attr(data-bg-color);
}```

